data.description: Welcome to your perfect starter home! Situated on a spacious 6,780 square foot lot in a peaceful neighborhood, this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is tailor-made for first-time buyers looking to embark on their homeownership journey. The generous backyard offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities, from gardening to hosting BBQs with friends and family, providing a sanctuary to unwind and enjoy the fresh air. Whether you're dreaming of cozy family dinners or summer evenings spent in the backyard, this home is ready to welcome you with open arms.Don't miss out on the opportunity to make it yours!
